  "body": "First of all, thank you for building this great tool.\r\n\r\nA couple of things aren't clear to me from the (otherwise excellent) documentation:\r\n1. Is it possible to do a voluntary exit then reactivate the validator (ie, if i know my node needs to go offline for a few days)?\r\n2. After the merge, how can we use a BLS withdrawal keypair to withdraw staked eth?\r\n\r\nStaking is a big commitment and I'd feel much more comfortable diving in if I saw some public documentation (either lighthouse-specific, or general) that clarifies those two issues, but I can't find any.\r\n",
